<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 12:27:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>牙科植入物制造商Straumann预计中国需求将提高2025年增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/dental-implant-maker-straumann-expects-china-demand-lift-2025-growth-2025-02-19/</link><description>瑞士牙科植入物制造商Straumann Hold Hold Hold Hold Hold预计，中国的需求有助于今年有助于提高销售增长，此前报告说，与市场估计相匹配的2024年收入后，它在周三表示。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 12:12:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/dental-implant-maker-straumann-expects-china-demand-lift-2025-growth-2025-02-19/</guid></item><item><title>苹果推出新的低成本iPhone以捕捉更广阔的市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-launch-new-lower-cost-iphone-capture-broader-market-2025-02-19/</link><description>苹果公司将于周三推出最新的iPhone模型，因为它希望获得更大的中档智能手机市场的份额，并抵御三星和中国华为等竞争对手的竞争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 12:00:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-launch-new-lower-cost-iphone-capture-broader-market-2025-02-19/</guid></item><item><title>早上竞标：落后于我们仍然与新高点调情</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-02-19/</link><description>看看美国和迈克·多兰（Mike Dolan）的全球市场的前一天</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 11:09:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-02-19/</guid></item><item><title>脂肪，不是肌肉：在比赛中为下一个减肥突破的制药者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/fat-not-muscle-drugmakers-race-next-weight-loss-breakthrough-2025-02-19/</link><description>当前的减肥方法，例如生活方式的改变，手术和流行的疗法，例如Novo Nordisk的Wegovy和Eli Lilly的Zepbough，导致脂肪和肌肉损失都会增加跌倒的风险并降低整体力量，这可能对老年患者特别有害。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 11:09:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/fat-not-muscle-drugmakers-race-next-weight-loss-breakthrough-2025-02-19/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯赞扬特朗普说北约是乌克兰战争的主要原因</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-praises-trump-saying-nato-was-major-cause-war-ukraine-2025-02-19/</link><description>俄罗斯外交部长谢尔盖·拉夫罗夫（Sergei Lavrov）周三赞扬美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，美国以前对乌克兰加入北约军事联盟的支持是乌克兰战争的主要原因。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 10:32:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-praises-trump-saying-nato-was-major-cause-war-ukraine-2025-02-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国的商业创新者说，与XI会面后将抵抗外部压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-business-innovators-say-will-resist-external-pressure-after-meeting-with-2025-02-19/</link><description>在习近平总统和私营部门之间罕见的会议之后，中国的一些著名商业领导人，包括汽车制造商Byd和小米的负责人表示，他们将抵抗外部压力并继续创新。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 10:22:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-business-innovators-say-will-resist-external-pressure-after-meeting-with-2025-02-19/</guid></item><item><title>由于技术兴趣不断上升，蚂蚁集团进入中国不断增长的人形机器人行业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/ant-group-enters-chinas-growing-humanoid-robot-industry-amid-rising-tech-2025-02-19/</link><description>Ant Group是与阿里巴巴相关的金融科技巨头，正在进入人形机器人行业，加入了越来越多的中国主要科技公司探索这一新兴领域的清单。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 10:14:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/ant-group-enters-chinas-growing-humanoid-robot-industry-amid-rising-tech-2025-02-19/</guid></item><item><title>股票靠近创纪录的高点，摆脱了特朗普的最新关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-wrapup-1-2025-02-19/</link><description>周三，全球股票在创纪录的高点上保持稳定，因为交易员谨慎地耸了耸肩，唐纳德·特朗普对汽车，半导体和药品进口的最新关税威胁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 10:10:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-wrapup-1-2025-02-19/</guid></item><item><title>一月份，外国直接投资对中国的投资下降了13.4％/年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/foreign-direct-investment-into-china-falls-134-yy-january-2025-02-19/</link><description>中国商务部周三表示，对中国的外国直接投资为1月份的976亿元人民币（1,340亿美元），比上一年下降了13.4％。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 09:47:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/foreign-direct-investment-into-china-falls-134-yy-january-2025-02-19/</guid></item><item><title>对冲基金在中国裁缝双赢的赌注</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hedge-funds-tailor-win-win-bets-china-2025-02-19/</link><description>全球对冲基金热衷于在美国 - 中国贸易紧张局势中驾驶的基金正在积累中国的股票投注，以期，如果北京与唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）构成协议，或者世界其他地区和中国对美国总统团结一致。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 09:38:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hedge-funds-tailor-win-win-bets-china-2025-02-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国反对越南在南中国海有争议的珊瑚礁的建设工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opposes-vietnams-building-work-disputed-reef-south-china-sea-2025-02-19/</link><description>中国外交部周三表示，中国反对越南在南中国海的一个有争议的胰岛上的建设活动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 09:21:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opposes-vietnams-building-work-disputed-reef-south-china-sea-2025-02-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国判决前国际政府行政长官死于遭受贿赂的缓刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-sentences-former-icbc-executive-death-with-reprieve-taking-bribes-2025-02-19/</link><description>国家广播公司周三报道说，中国已判处中国工业和商业银行前副总裁张洪利（Zhang Hongli）死亡，遭受了为期两年的贿赂。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 09:18:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-sentences-former-icbc-executive-death-with-reprieve-taking-bribes-2025-02-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国最高金融监管机构向私人公司发誓稳定的信贷供应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-top-financial-regulator-vows-stable-credit-supply-private-firms-2025-02-19/</link><description>一份正式声明显示，中国最高金融监管机构誓言，它将为私人公司维持稳定有效的信贷供应，并将加强对贷款的支持。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 09:05:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-top-financial-regulator-vows-stable-credit-supply-private-firms-2025-02-19/</guid></item><item><title>山东退出亚洲冠军联赛之前</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/shandong-withdraw-asian-champions-league-before-ulsan-fixture-2025-02-19/</link><description>中国超级联赛球队山东·泰桑（Shandong Taishan）在周三对阵乌尔桑HD的最后一场比赛前几个小时就退出了亚洲冠军联赛精英。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 08:44:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/shandong-withdraw-asian-champions-league-before-ulsan-fixture-2025-02-19/</guid></item><item><title>在平衡风险和奖励方面，中国将在2月不变的贷款利率不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/balancing-risks-rewards-china-set-leave-lending-rates-unchanged-feb-2025-02-19/</link><description>路透社一项民意调查显示，预计中国将在周四保持基准贷款利率不变，因为当局在优先考虑财务稳定性和在北京面临新的贸易紧张局势的时候提供了更多的刺激。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 07:54:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/balancing-risks-rewards-china-set-leave-lending-rates-unchanged-feb-2025-02-19/</guid></item></channel></rss>